Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏘～這裡有隻妖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜{\rsymbol}…{\r}夜斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個反應很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厭惡和恐懼很容易劃出境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,境界線?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器唯一能使用的矛 以及盾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這陣子工作中表現不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誇我對你也沒好處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先用手指做出矛的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在妖和自己之間劃一條線試試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 這就是境界線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是分隔自己與其他的線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖無法跨越它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗也會這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:00:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,境界線是專屬於神器的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然任何一個神器都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但初次就能有如此強的分隔力{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我認識的神器中也是前所未有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗認識的神器{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}被夜斗稱作野良的那個人也是神器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是{\rsymbol}…{\r}隨便玩玩的女人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君由我來照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和那邊肯定不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗身邊是最不能呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就無家可歸過不上正經生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上原女友 不倫戀 隨便玩玩的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個接一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太齷齪了 沒資格當監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君寄住在我家最合適了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離・遠・點・啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 刺得我痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開你那滿是汗的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒看雪音君很不樂意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你瞧{\rsymbol}…{\r}啊刺到了刺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺得我痛死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底是怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過啊 這小子一旦動歪念頭我就會痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歪念頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤男寡女住在同一屋簷下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音肯定滿腦子冒限制級的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦限制級的是某個運動衫男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君可是好孩子 完全不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 雪音君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別去啊 雪音
Comment: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【境界線】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和是富家大小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話呢 我只是普通初中生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得一點都不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你的父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 今天他們正好要晚回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 那豈不是就我們兩個{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君 噓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐{\rsymbol}…{\r}佐佐木阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡水已經熱好了 想泡隨時可以泡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間雪音君隨便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是日和的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個大我很多的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這房間最近沒在用 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和有哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間就在隔壁 有事就叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和真是好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,計劃順利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這個狀況 就能瞞著幫工的佐佐木阿姨和父母{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 歡迎回{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 我買了蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他媽 工作結束能喝一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為這個而活的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說老公 手洗了嗎{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 偷吃零嘴太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是下意識地{\rsymbol}…{\r}下意識地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和的媽媽真敏銳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不露餡 我也來有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我帶走雪音君豈不是沒了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 那傢伙怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是要跟著夜斗去睡路邊的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與這房子不同 神社或祠堂屬於神域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡可以不受妖的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚讓棲息於黑暗中的妖開始活動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是誕生魔的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是那傢伙 恐怕承受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久沒泡過熱水澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙{\rsymbol}…{\r}我要是一直不在他身邊 會怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會去用那個女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話{\rsymbol}…{\r}我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 這氣味在哪裡聞過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 這是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日日{\rsymbol}…{\r}日日日日日{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和剛剛泡過的洗澡水?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 忘在這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 日和 快點該你洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:09:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,股四頭肌{\rsymbol}…{\r}要加強鍛煉{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我房間的燈被你老爸關掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周圍一黑 我就安心不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一起睡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這{\rsymbol}…{\r}這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 很冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可可可可{\rsymbol}…{\r}可是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒和別人一起睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雪音君也好好聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 很喜歡這個氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在身邊聞到 就會很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪～音～君～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 為什麼你在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼為什麼 你這小色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 那是日和叫我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人對你來說還太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在跟著我就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耍什麼帥啊 運動衫男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也有嗎 和我一樣是神器的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜也時化起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離鬧市區 0.9
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0.7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六點鐘方向 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你陪我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正沒別的事可做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天還會繼續變涼呢 買來也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等{\rsymbol}…{\r}不用啦 我什麼都不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這點東西就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧 人們都沒看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非要用的話悄悄借一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 雪音君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做和小偷沒區別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 給我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想要的就跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗 你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情不好 正在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好照顧那孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他好像又做了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜{\rsymbol}…{\r}夜斗是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過吧 神明和神器是一心同體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君若生心魔 我身上會有刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明和神器的關係 就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 夜斗在偷我父親酒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君也被刺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心生邪念產生的痛苦 只會從神器傳給神明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是單向通行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器原本是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是人類 就會犯下罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨 恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒 焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷 慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些舉不盡的例子 都會生心魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這罪孽將變為痛苦 通過神器教會我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何謂善惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先打消你一個誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,善惡雖由人定 但神明並無此概念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以做任何事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便是傷害任何人 殺死任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天也要教訓一下雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用神明的裁決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經斬過神器的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會斬人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找雪音君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落下了這麼大個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和還在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 都這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 要找個{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要找個不黑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 大家都無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有眼球怪物過來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在等媽媽的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是補習班結束之後就會來接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是{\rsymbol}…{\r}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我等到6點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到媽媽來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 媽媽要來晚些了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥家裡人也很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個{\rsymbol}…{\r}我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 等媽媽來了用車送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以再等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概 不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐 還說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的媽媽 在我家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君 用夜斗教的那招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手指做出矛形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 剛才說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 它們過不了那條線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香 好香 好香{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:19:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香 好香{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香 再讓我多聞聞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖{\rsymbol}…{\r}把女孩子拉了進去{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救那傢伙啊 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 雪器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豐葦原之中津國中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒亂無度的彼岸之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾 夜斗神顯聖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此雪器斬碎降服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將業障重重之穢跡{\rsymbol}…{\r}盡數祓除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要救她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子已經完全被妖同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經只能斬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被妖所障 所吞噬的靈魂將要面臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有充滿了詛咒的活地獄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要解放那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在市內巡邏的囷巴發來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是看到了正在斬妖的夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貌似還得到了新的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
